==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inconvincible
<hw>In`con*vin"ci*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inconvincibilis</ets>. See <er>In-</er> not, and
<er>Convince</er>.]</ety> <def>Not convincible; incapable of being
convinced.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>None are so <qex>inconvincible</qex> as your half-witted
people.</q> <rj><qau>Gov. of the Tongue.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inconvincibly</ent>⟦br⟧
